data.message: If anyone would like more information, please message me!

message:
Are you interested in ....
doing ministry on the beach?
getting a (paid) internship for the summer?
experiencing ministry in the inner city?
reaching out to millennials and hipsters?
growing in your understanding and experience of racial and ethnic diversity?
getting a job while on summer mission?
urban church planting and growth?
working with adorable children?
being trained and equipped to minister to your peers on campus?
experiencing living life on mission in an urban setting ?
... then check out Milwaukee Summer Mission, the Summer Mission that fuses a classic Cru summer mission with a stirring Cru Inner City ministry experience
